These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, chef
1. the project-manager is in an even position##4
2. the chef is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku |
| Job     | chef    | project-manager   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | sprite | 7up        |
| Sport      | lacrosse  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: british, italian
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | techno |
| Nationality   | british | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, garlic
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | coffee      | soy-milk |
| Food       | raspberry | garlic    |

 #################################

 
