.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | handball | weightlifting  |
| Transport   | van  | roller |

